o-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\">学校国标代码：</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\">12621   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"p0\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\">第五条</span></b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\">学校地址：广州市增城区荔城街华商路一号；邮政编码：</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\">511300   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"p0\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\">第六条</span></b><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\">办学层次：本科</span><span style=\"FONT-FAM